text: Acanthodactylus lacrymae is a species of lizard in the family Lacertidae. The species is endemic to Morocco. ==References== Category:Acanthodactylus Category:Reptiles described in 2020 Category:Taxa named by Aurélien Miralles Category:Taxa named by Philippe Geniez Category:Taxa named by Menad Beddek Category:Taxa named by Daniel Mendez-Aranda Category:Taxa named by José C.
